# Showcase

This page demonstrates page-level frontmatter overrides in action:

- `layout: default`
- `theme: pycorino`
- `width: wide`

@callout .ok
  This is useful for landing pages that need a different visual tone than technical docs.
@end callout

@hero .accent
  # Build pages that feel different
  Mix layout directives with per-page theme/layout settings to create distinct sections inside one site.
@end hero

